{"tid":1931164,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"右腳痛左幾日 痛到生不如死","createTime":"2020-03-18T04:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T08:04:51.000Z","uid":72226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a87e0f9025a6aea4ed7d40adfb5daecf3fd756ba","tid":1931164,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食咗止痛藥有時會好咗少少<br />\n應唔應該睇醫生？<br />\n定還是呢啲係過幾個禮拜就會好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻腳一行路就超痛<br />\n訓係張床度都有少少痛<br />\n果晚無聊喺度拍隻腳 之後半夜就突然超痛<br />\n唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇好似係腳底筋膜炎<br />\n有冇人知應該要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生定還是等佢自己好<br />\n依家行路都要就住就住<br />\n如果唔係就右腳超痛"},{"pid":"d37c9522faee01b29799f40d55214c466e1a9e1e","tid":1931164,"uid":29218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"果晚無聊喺度拍隻腳 之後半夜就突然超痛???<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b622289a1b2baab49eb06612c25e1eada4056a","tid":1931164,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"半夜痛？係未食得太好？"},{"pid":"1858d94d106f37f7840f794cbef8780767de55b2","tid":1931164,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37c9522faee01b29799f40d55214c466e1a9e1e","tid":1931164,"uid":29218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"果晚無聊喺度拍隻腳 之後半夜就突然超痛???<br />\n<br />